Rainbow Bed Foam and beyond

Rainbow Foam Factory

Rainbow Foam and Plastic Industry is a private Limited company that produces polyurethane foam in Addis Ababa, Ethiopia.
It was founded and established in 1996 by Mr. Abeselom Yehdego and his wife Almaz Yacob as a private limited company.

Foam Products

Foam products at Rainbow are polyurethane based and are available in many different sizes, shapes and density. Our foams are strong, versatile and easy to use.

Custom Orders

At Rainbow Industry, we do all of our manufacturing in-house, we have a lot of flexibility when it comes to custom orders, including the ability to use custom patterns.
